# ROADMAP (Domain)

Owner: Domain Architect (DA)

Purpose: a single, developer-facing plan for this domain that reconciles multiple upstream inputs into stable implementation targets.

Optional: provide a machine-readable roll-up in `ROADMAP.yml` (same directory) so Solution Architects can aggregate domain roadmaps without parsing Markdown.

Authoring contract:
- Humans edit `ROADMAP.md` only.
- Tools/skills generate `ROADMAP.yml` from this file (do not hand-edit `ROADMAP.yml`).

